lead_paragraph: Scott Dunlap shot a 3-under 69 in the second round to take a two-shot lead at the Mississippi Gulf Resort Classic on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Dunlap Shoots 3-Under 69, Takes Two-Shot Lead at MGRC
